      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      80                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      04                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "DISTINTA DI INVIO FATTURE 'XML' NR."
                                          to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
